description:
X2UTermination:  Records of X2U terminations including timestamp, location, cell and termination identifiers.

dateTime: Timestamp of the X2U termination event.
Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the termination occurred.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell involved in the X2U termination.
Id2: Redundant identifier, likely mirroring CellId.
Id3:  Ancillary identifier (purpose unclear from sample data).
vsDataType:  Specifies the data type as X2U termination data.
vsDataFormatVersion:  Version of the Ericsson-specific data format.
X2UTermination.x2UTerminationId: Unique identifier for this specific X2U termination record.
